              |                                                                                 
              v                                                                                 
 == rwl.schedule_append(ops) ==  multi-thread                                                   
  |            
  |                                                             
  ---> need_schedule = rwl.m_ops_to_append.emty() !&& rwl.m_appending 
  |            
  |            
  ---> rwl.m_ops_to_append.push_back(ops)
  |                                                                                                    
  ------------------------->--------------------------------------------                                                          
