         |         |                                                                                                                         |      |     
         |         ---> if current entry is completed and current in-flight flush is reasonable, it can be flushed.                          |      |     
         |                                                                                                                                   |      |                             
         v                                                                                                                                   |      |                     
         ---> == construct_flush_entry_ctx() ==                                                                                              |      |             
